<p>
<a name="">@HI{{@EM{{shunkanteki}}}}</a> is an adverb that refers to something that is brief or instantaneous, occurring within a moment or a very short period of time.
It often conveys the sense of something that lasts only for an instant or is experienced in the blink of an eye.

